    {
      "text": "Signal (stylized as SIGNAL) is an otome game released on December 3, 2009 by D3 Publisher for Nintendo DS, in both a standard and a limited edition. It is part of a series including the PlayStation 2 game Darling Special Backlash Koi no Exhaust Heat (Darling Special Backlash 恋のエキゾースト・ヒート), sequel to the PC game Darling. Its CERO rating is D (17+).",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『SIGNAL』（シグナル）は、2009年12月3日にディースリー・パブリッシャーからニンテンドーDS用に発売された女性向け恋愛アドベンチャーゲーム。",
      "lang": "ja",
